</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_31" id="15r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_31_r1l15">Byſchof von Eyſtet / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_31_r1l16"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Vns hat fürbracht her Hans vicarier in ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l17">Morıcʒen kappellen bey vns cʒü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> kapplan / vvie Jm die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l18"><expan>korh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / deʒ Newenſtifts cʒü Spalt / leppgeding ſchuldig ſein / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l19">daʒ ſie Jm etlıche Jare / vnd langcʒeit ver cʒogen vnd nicht gerichtet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l20"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . darvmb er ſie für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> Official gen Eyſtet auf geıſtlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l21">gerichte <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l22">kapplan beholffen ſein vvöllet / daʒ Jm das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>uallen</expan> <expan>leipg<ex>eding</ex></expan> gütlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l23">gerichtet 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </del> / vnd auch fürbas nicht mer <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / . Alſo daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l24">Jm ein benüg geſchehe nach <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> brief lawt die er von Jn hat / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_31_r1l28">ob 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſie </del> des 
<add><ab facs="#facs_31_line_1571150340310_995">dıe <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>korh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab></add> ſüſt nicht tün <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade / mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Official </ab>
